{"tid":2023770,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪有連登效應。我預期樓市未來必定會升唔會大跌","createTime":"2020-05-19T08:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T15:17:21.000Z","uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f843df09c00f418050774d0bf544011dcabebc21","tid":2023770,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uks7Zch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUks7Zch.jpg&h=857f69a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓價負擔指數由11年大升至20年<br />\n等於香港人實質收入大跌一半<br />\n如果未來所有因素不變<br />\n支那繼續大印銀紙<br />\n香港樓價有機會再升多一倍<br />\n因為深圳負擔指數已經30倍<br />\n共產黨睇穿30倍都無人反抗或者反抗唔到<br />\n只要愚弄下人講下失業率維持低水平<br />\n出下打手話你班人自己唔夠勁<br />\n理論上唔怕繼續印鈔<br />\n所以我睇好香港同深圳樓價必定唔會大跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人工資10年間跌左一半 (以樓市購買力計算)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fssOfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fssOfS</a>"},{"pid":"573a3625afc6c24d850e9da7420a19dd4c7fbe73","tid":2023770,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:14:27.000Z","msg":"香港再出發，盡快開關<br />\n樓市火箭式報復式上升gogogo<br />\n劏房盡快炒返上千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d736b3e0c6af4571a5ace959225410094ab210c","tid":2023770,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"不嬲連燈都燈神<br />\n你見之前買油都跣左一大班人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1527b07c66dda03d7950c12420a8485a1a73537","tid":2023770,"uid":321157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"我僅以至誠相信樓市唔會跌、支那唔會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9dd2abce76b0f2016b4511379ee0e7802b34b8","tid":2023770,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1527b07c66dda03d7950c12420a8485a1a73537","tid":2023770,"uid":321157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"我僅以至誠相信樓市唔會跌、支那唔會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:17:01.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n中共係唔會短期內倒台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c71bd3c01ae538fb0a6d362a982a2371f4ab4f","tid":2023770,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d736b3e0c6af4571a5ace959225410094ab210c","tid":2023770,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"不嬲連燈都燈神<br />\n你見之前買油都跣左一大班人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:18:26.000Z","msg":"樓市必定唔會大跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人話沙士重臨會大跌<br />\n結果又燈<br />\n證明核爆都唔跌<br />\n同700騰訊一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話之你30，40倍年收入<br />\n都唔會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc217a764b49d0c00939ddfb7d34a684ffca2ef","tid":2023770,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:20:22.000Z","msg":"匯豐無可能1年內上返60蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5532abcebab2af43fbf34382f5aff1d4e33f8919","tid":2023770,"uid":77905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"係咪搞錯咗<br />\n連登似乎好友多過淡淡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd0aa034b438a9b3e78b75a131270e2826e6e54","tid":2023770,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5532abcebab2af43fbf34382f5aff1d4e33f8919","tid":2023770,"uid":77905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"係咪搞錯咗<br />\n連登似乎好友多過淡淡 <img sr